{"tid":1823943,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"又有和你寄！","createTime":"2020-01-14T05:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T09:48:26.000Z","uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1745b214d7875e30b14322a318ef2bad4b264829","tid":1823943,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:36:03.000Z","msg":"不割蓆不分化<br />\n但係今日就要你做分化戰線<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">係分化小粉紅呀</span></span><br />\n之前有手足發起和你寄freehk xmas card得到好多外國人同議員迴響<br />\n而家就要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">將反共文宣寄去中国，由佢地內部傳開中共既仆街野</span></span><br />\n文宣應該大幅圖，文字精簡，要好似長輩圖有針對性，唔洗講大道理架<br />\n令小粉紅懷疑人生懷疑黨就得架啦<br />\n例如：好值得煲大既武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\n成日話輸出革命，唔通仲等5毛翻牆嗌交呀<br />\n緊係主動出擊去分化敵人嗌<br />\n真係驚比人check到指模既咪全程戴手套囉<br />\n用埋電腦print地址就更加睇唔到字跡<br />\n得閒就sip落郵筒，幾乎係零成本（郵票有限錢姐）<br />\n如果每個人都幾十張咁寄，截得到咁多咩<br />\n咁叻咪截晒香港寄去鄰国既信囉<br />\n<br />\n負評請比原因/改善方法"},{"pid":"efaee1520a0f147413d4fbb72b831bd33a81a8c6","tid":1823943,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:48:01.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a32df1a7ac0618777cc2776107d23963d7047e4","tid":1823943,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:48:12.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ed373c84e20c0367a24f9f78adbbaf1b1a2734","tid":1823943,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:48:26.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}